data.title: Register of Members Interests Dáil TDs 2007
data.meta_description: Register of Members Interests Dáil TDs 2007 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is a register of interests for members of the Dáil Éireann (Irish parliament) covering the period from January 1, 2007 to December 31, 2007. It provides information on the occupational income, shares, directorships, land holdings, gifts, property, travel facilities, remunerated positions, and contracts for each member. The register includes entries for several members, including Bertie Ahern, Dermot Ahern, and Sean Barrett, listing details about their financial interests as required by ethics laws.
